decision_conditions:
&lt;p&gt;Detailed drawings and full particulars of the following shall be submitted to and approved in
writing by the Local Planning Authority before the start of the relevant part of the works. The
works shall not be carried out otherwise than in accordance with the details thus approved:
a. Details of the structural supports to the rear wall on the No. 10 side (we have no detail on
what these might be) in the form of a brief description and a sketch drawing;
b. Details of proposed works to windows including a window schedule and full details (1:20
elevations, 1:5 sections of all frames and 1:1 sections of glazing bars and units) of any
replacement windows;
c. Details of all new and replacement internal and external doors;
d. Details of all new and replacement internal joinery;
e. Details of works of fireproofing between floors in the form of a brief description and a
typical sketch section with dimensions and materials shown;
f. Details of rainwater goods in the form of a manufacturerâ€™s specification;
g. Details of ground surface materials to the front and rear gardens and steps.
REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to protecting the special architectural and
historic interest and integrity of the building&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
